# Architecture Diagrams

## High-Level Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Presentation Layer"
        FE[Frontend<br/>Vite + TypeScript]
        API[REST API<br/>FastAPI]
        CLI_P[CLI<br/>Click]
    end

    subgraph "Application Layer"
        CMD[Commands]
        QRY[Queries]
        DTO[DTOs]
        SVC[Services]
    end

    subgraph "Domain Layer"
        ENT[Entities]
        VO[Value Objects]
        EVT[Domain Events]
    end

    subgraph "Infrastructure Layer"
{%- if database_backend == 'postgresql' %}
        DB[(PostgreSQL)]
{%- elif database_backend == 'sqlite' %}
        DB[(SQLite)]
{%- endif %}
        ORM[ORM Models]
        REPO[Repositories]
{%- if use_redis %}
        CACHE[(Redis Cache)]
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_celery %}
        QUEUE[Celery Workers]
{%- endif %}
    end

    FE --> API
    API --> CMD
    API --> QRY
    CLI_P --> CMD
    CMD --> SVC
    QRY --> DTO
    SVC --> ENT
    ENT --> VO
    ENT --> EVT
    REPO --> ORM
    ORM --> DB
    SVC -.->|Port| REPO
{%- if use_redis %}
    SVC -.->|Port| CACHE
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_celery %}
    SVC -.->|Port| QUEUE
{%- endif %}
```

## Hexagonal Architecture (Ports & Adapters)

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Driving Adapters (Left)"
        HTTP[HTTP API]
        CLI_A[CLI]
        EVENTS_IN[Event Handlers]
    end

    subgraph "Application Core"
        subgraph "Ports In"
            PI1[Repository Port]
            PI2[Cache Port]
            PI3[EventBus Port]
            PI4[UoW Port]
        end

        subgraph "Domain"
            D1[Entities]
            D2[Value Objects]
            D3[Domain Events]
        end

        subgraph "Use Cases"
            U1[Commands]
            U2[Queries]
        end
    end

    subgraph "Driven Adapters (Right)"
        DB_A[(Database)]
{%- if use_redis %}
        REDIS_A[(Redis)]
{%- endif %}
        MEM_A[In-Memory]
        HTTP_OUT[HTTP Client]
{%- if use_celery %}
        CELERY_A[Celery]
{%- endif %}
    end

    HTTP --> U1
    HTTP --> U2
    CLI_A --> U1
    EVENTS_IN --> U1
    U1 --> D1
    U2 --> D1
    D1 --> D2
    D1 --> D3
    PI1 -.-> DB_A
{%- if use_redis %}
    PI2 -.-> REDIS_A
{%- endif %}
    PI2 -.-> MEM_A
    PI3 -.-> MEM_A
{%- if use_celery %}
    PI3 -.-> CELERY_A
{%- endif %}
```

