{%- endif %}
{%- endif %}
{%- endif %}
```

## Data Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant A as API Router
    participant U as Use Case
    participant R as Repository
    participant D as Database

    C->>A: HTTP Request
    A->>U: Execute command/query
    U->>R: Access data (via port)
    R->>D: SQL query
    D-->>R: Result set
    R-->>U: Domain entity
    U-->>A: DTO response
    A-->>C: HTTP Response
```
